@startuml
actor User
participant "ProductPage (UI)" as UI
participant "API Service" as API
participant "ProductController" as PC
participant "ProductService" as PS
participant "ProductRepository" as PR
database "MongoDB" as DB

User -> UI : Truy cập trang danh mục / Chọn danh mục
UI -> API : GET /api/products?category={categoryId}&page={page}&limit={limit}
API -> PC : searchProducts(req)
PC -> PS : searchProducts(filters, sort, page, limit)
PS -> PR : searchAndFilter(filters, sort, skip, limit)
PR -> DB : Product.find(query).skip(skip).limit(limit)
DB --> PR : productsData
PR -> DB : Product.countDocuments(query)
DB --> PR : totalCount
PR --> PS : { products, total }
PS --> PC : { products, total }
PC --> API : JSON { status: 'success', data: { products, total } }
API --> UI : Hiển thị sản phẩm ban đầu

User -> UI : Kéo xuống cuối trang (Lazy Loading)
UI -> API : GET /api/products?category={categoryId}&page={page+1}&limit={limit}
API -> PC : searchProducts(req)
... (các bước tương tự) ...
PC --> UI : JSON { products, total }
UI -> UI : Append sản phẩm mới vào danh sách hiện tại
@enduml
